-- Nigeria's Sterling Bank first-quarter profit rises 17 pct
-- By Oludare Mayowa
-- Tue Apr 22, 2014 07:57AM EDT
-- None



LAGOS, April 22 (Reuters) - Nigeria's Sterling Bank <STERLNB.LG> said on Tuesday its first-quarter pretax profit rose to 3.54 billion naira ($21.8 million), up 17.3 percent from 3.02 billion naira a year earlier.

